                    In hair loss condition, each hair cycle will produce thinner, weaker and fewer hair. In time,
                    follicles begin to die and hair fails to regrow.
                </p>
                <p class="text-orange lead">
                    <strong class="font-weight-bold">So yes, hair thinning is a sign of early stage hair loss.</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
